    "comment": "Rationale: \"mAb-GlyRβ revealed immunoreactive puncta along the dendrites and on the somata of SCNs. B-D: Double-labeling with mAb-GlyRβ and a VIAAT antibody revealed significant apposition of GlyRβ puncta to inhibitory nerve terminals. E-G: Additionally, GlyRβ staining colocalized with gephyrin clusters detected by a polyclonal antibody.\"\n\n18/02/2021 Dnyanada: The high degree of colocalisation of GlyRβ puncta with gephyrin make it suitable for a specific ontology term \"postsynaptic specialization\" (previously annotated to the term \"synapse\").. Experimental description: \"Synaptic localization of mAb-GlyRβ immunoreactivity in cultured rat spinal neurons\"",
